WEBVTT

00:11:00.120 --> 00:11:03.816
When it comes to brutal murderers
who post their beheading videos,

00:11:03.840 --> 00:11:07.536
the Internet has created
a new kind of crowd.

00:11:07.560 --> 00:11:12.576
Today, the action takes place
in a distant time and place,

00:11:12.600 --> 00:11:15.896
which gives the viewer a sense
of detachment from what's happening,

00:11:15.920 --> 00:11:17.176
a sense of separation.

00:11:17.200 --> 00:11:18.936
It's nothing to do with me.

00:11:18.960 --> 00:11:20.240
It's already happened.

00:11:21.400 --> 00:11:24.936
We are also offered
an unprecedented sense of intimacy.

00:11:24.960 --> 00:11:27.656
Today, we are all offered front row seats.

00:11:27.680 --> 00:11:31.416
We can all watch in private,
in our own time and space,